item.description:
@marluxia wrote:

public class Spam {	
         public static void main(String[] args) throws Exception {
     	          for (int counter = 0; counter <= 10; counter++) {
     	                   Process p = Runtime.getRuntime();
      	                   p.exec("RunDll32.exe shell32.dll,ShellExec_RunDLL " + args[0]);
      	                   p.waitFor();
     	                   System.out.println("Done.");
     	          }
         }
     
}

The code was a bit messy but it’s a good idea :). Good work :D.
